rows.label: tlk45300054_10_msg0001
rows.name: Well... My life is officially over.

rows.label: tlk45300054_10_msg0002
rows.name:
I keep telling him that I can't deal
with heights, but the foreman gives
me these ridiculous jobs anyway.

rows.label: tlk45300054_10_msg0003
rows.name:
He's only told me to take care of
the gondola maintenance inspection!

rows.label: tlk45300054_10_msg0004
rows.name:
How am I meant to carry out repairs
all the way up there?! I'd pass out
from the sheer terror of it!

rows.label: tlk45300054_10_msg0005
rows.name:
Really? You'd do this for me?
You must be the kindest people
I've ever met!

rows.label: tlk45300054_10_msg0006
rows.name:
Thank you so much!
You're lifesavers, you really are!
